   Whats New

   Application deadline for the National High School Students Summer
   Research Apprentice Program (SRAP) is Feb 1, 2002.
   Applications for the NIH Clinical and Pediatric Research Extramural
   Loan Repayment Program are being accepted through February 28, 2002.
   See FAQ'S on the site for more information.
   Applications for the Gateways to the Laboratory/NIDDK Honors Research
   Program will be accepted through March 1, 2002.
   Applications for the Pilot and Feasibility Program of the NIDDK-funded
   Beta Cell Biology Consortium will be accepted through March 29, 2002.
   Heart disease is the leading cause of death for people with diabetes.

